OL,3,CUS student guilty of murdering
OL,4,C'germophobic' lover
OL,6,FFellow student Joshua Michals, 26,
OL,7,Ftold his trial at the Old Bailey that
OL,8,FMs Wang was "germophobic" and became
OL,9,F"stressed", believing, incorrectly,
OL,10,Fthat she had contracted a sexually
OL,11,Ftransmitted disease (STD) after they
OL,12,Fhad sex.
OL,14,FA jury found Michals guilty of murder
OL,15,Fon Monday after 16-and-a-half hours of
OL,16,Fdeliberations.
OL,18,FDuring the trial, prosecutor Henrietta
OL,19,FPaget KC said Michals had "flown into
OL,20,Fa rage" and killed Ms Wang after
OL,21,Fmeeting her at her flat.
