OL,6,FThey had first met on the Goldsmiths
OL,7,Fcampus and began an on-and-off casual
OL,8,Frelationship in 2023.
OL,10,FMichals told jurors he had felt "so-
OL,11,Fso" about pursuing a relationship with
OL,12,FMs Wang because she had a phobia of
OL,13,Fgerms.
OL,15,FAfter finding a "red dot" on her skin
OL,16,Fafter sex, she demanded he get an STD
OL,17,Ftest, even vowing to find him on
OL,18,Fcampus to "drag" him to see a GP, the
OL,19,Fcourt previously heard.
