OL,6,FThe student said he went to her flat
OL,7,Fon March 20 2024 with a charcuterie
OL,8,Fselection to bring some "normalcy" to
OL,9,Fthe "bizarre situation".
OL,11,FHe claimed that when he arrived at the
OL,12,Fflat in Lewisham, he found Ms Wang
OL,13,F"cold" and monosyllabic, and that she
OL,14,Fattacked him with a knife as he came
OL,15,Fout of the bathroom.
OL,17,FA post-mortem examination found Ms
OL,18,FWang died from stab wounds to the head
OL,19,Fand compression to the neck, the trial
OL,20,Fheard.
