OL,6,FMichals previously told jurors he did
OL,7,Fnot mean to strike Ms Wang with the
OL,8,Fknife, saying: "I just wanted to get
OL,9,Fher away from me."
OL,11,FHe also said he pressed his forearm to
OL,12,Fher neck to try to restrain her and he
OL,13,Fdid not mean to kill her or cause her
OL,14,Fharm.
OL,16,FMichals called his father after the
OL,17,Fincident and obtained the details for
OL,18,Fa solicitor before going to his own
OL,19,Fflat and calling 999, the trial heard.
