OL,6,FHe also took Ms Wang's phone from her
OL,7,Fkitchen and put it in a bin outside,
OL,8,Fjurors were previously told.It was
OL,9,Frecovered days later at a refuse area
OL,10,Fin Newham, east London.
OL,12,FJurors have been told that Michals
OL,13,Fnever had a sexually transmitted
OL,14,Fdisease.
OL,16,FBorn and raised in Chicago, Illinois,
OL,17,FMichals studied film-making at
OL,18,Funiversity before moving to London to
OL,19,Fpursue a year-long master's degree at
OL,20,FGoldsmiths.
