OL,6,FThe London university paid tribute to
OL,7,FZhe Wang following the verdict,
OL,8,Fdeploring the loss of "a remarkable
OL,9,Fwriter" whose work will be published
OL,10,Fposthumously in an upcoming Goldsmiths
OL,11,Fanthology.
OL,13,FDr Francis Gilbert, senior lecturer in
OL,14,Fthe School of Mind, Body and Society
OL,15,Fat Goldsmiths, said: "We are devasted
OL,16,Fby the loss of Zhe Wang, who was a
OL,17,Fwonderful student, a remarkable writer
OL,18,Fand a thinker who combined deep
OL,19,Fintellectual curiosity with creative
OL,20,Fcourage and approached writing as a
OL,21,Fmindful practice.
OL,26,@pD@WOUqD@GO]wD@VOU
