OL,6,F"Her work blended Buddhist thought,
OL,7,Fimaginative storytelling and
OL,8,Freflective clarity in a way that
OL,9,Fmarked her out as a unique and
OL,10,Fsingular voice.
OL,12,F"She was preparing to publish her
OL,13,Fwork, and we will honour her
OL,14,Fintentions by including her writing in
OL,15,Fa forthcoming Goldsmiths anthology.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
