OL,6,F"Zhe was joyful, mindful and generous.
OL,7,FShe was deeply loved by her peers, who
OL,8,Fcontinue to speak of her gentleness,
OL,9,Fher humour and her thoughtful
OL,10,Fpresence. She made our community
OL,11,Fkinder and more attentive.
OL,13,F"Her classmates continue to mourn her
OL,14,Floss and remember her with profound
OL,15,Flove, recalling the warmth of her
OL,16,Fpresence and the inspiration she
OL,17,Foffered so generously to others.
OL,19,F"We will miss Zhe always.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU{D@AOU
