OL,6,F"Her writing continues to illuminate
OL,7,Four community, and her memory remains
OL,8,Fa source of tenderness, inspiration
OL,9,Fand care at Goldsmiths.
OL,11,F"We send again our profound
OL,12,Fcondolences to Zhe's family who
OL,13,Fgrieved with an intensity that
OL,14,Fexpressed the depth of their love for
OL,15,Fher.
OL,17,F"Her poem Ode To A Foolish Bee
OL,18,Fcaptures so much of what made Zhe's
OL,19,Fwriting distinctive: compassion,
OL,20,Fhumour, gentle insight and a desire to
OL,21,Fguide others without causing harm.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUyD@AOU
