OL,6,F"The exit beckons just above the pane,
OL,7,Fyet she flits in vain, causing a
OL,8,Fstrain.A towel in my hand, the gentle
OL,9,Fguide, trying not to harm, by her
OL,10,Fside.In her escape, she set herself
OL,11,Ffree."
OL,13,FMichals, of Deals Gateway, south-east
OL,14,FLondon, will be sentenced at a later
OL,15,Fdate.
